Description: citoMove is a wrapper for the cito R package. The 'cito' package provides a user-friendly interface for training and interpreting deep neural networks (DNN). The citoMove package extends cito with an interface to fit a conditional logit (clogit) likelihood with the purpose of fitting step selection function (ssf) models of animal movement.
